Why?

296
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,500
Guess.

297
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:45,980
It's because of you.

298
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,520
He practiced with you so much yesterday

299
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:48,580
that his hand got swollen.

300
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,720
Just did a few blocks.

301
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:52,780
So delicate.

302
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,780
Just did a few blocks?

303
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:57,260
He's been focused on you for the past few days.

304
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:00,840
Poor Gao Ge.

305
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:02,380
Such a thankless job.

306
00:16:11,840 --> 00:16:12,680
There he is.

307
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:17,880
You're looking for me?

308
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,440
This is for you.

309
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:25,380
So cheesy.

310
00:16:25,880 --> 00:16:26,720
Thanks.

311
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,080
By the way,

312
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:29,640
this is for you.

313
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:31,180
Consider it a reward

314
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:33,540
for overcoming your mental block.

315
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:37,160
No need. I'm using this.

316
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:38,800
- It's nice.
- Take it.

317
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:40,020
I don't need it.

318
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:47,020
Then take it back.

319
00:16:48,760 --> 00:16:49,660
Do what you want with it.

320
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:55,920
Thanks.

321
00:16:56,520 --> 00:16:57,360
Bye-bye.

322
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:01,500
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

323
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:05,040
This is your reward.

324
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:05,880
Take it.

325
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:07,880
Is it just a reward?

326
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:09,440
I came to give you medicine.

327
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:11,140
Can't you see my feelings for you?

328
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:13,020
Isn't it because I'm injured?

329
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:14,380
Do you mean...

330
00:17:15,120 --> 00:17:16,930
Oh, come on.

331
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,830
Are you two bored? So annoying.

332
00:17:18,830 --> 00:17:19,670
Oh, come on.

333
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,720
This is all Liqiang's idea.

334
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:23,040
I'm just playing along.

335
00:17:23,040 --> 00:17:24,440
You acted well just now.

336
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,720
Why did you pin it on me?

337
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:26,740
You two are so childish.

338
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,800
For pain and swelling?

339
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:34,260
This medicine is pretty spot-on.

340
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:37,120
Chen Weilan cares about you, Gao.

341
00:17:37,120 --> 00:17:38,180
Good for you.

342
00:17:39,320 --> 00:17:40,160
What does that mean?

343
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:41,880
What does that mean?

344
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:43,320
Even a fool can see it.

345
00:17:43,320 --> 00:17:44,500
She likes you.

346
00:17:44,840 --> 00:17:46,500
- Affirmed.
- You noticed?

347
00:17:51,820 --> 00:17:55,260
(You might have to repeat a year.)

348
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:01,280
Coach Lu is so weird.

349
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:02,440
He's been here for so long.

350
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:03,960
We're close to solving your problem,

351
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:05,100
yet he hasn't figured it out.

352
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:08,220
What problem?

353
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:09,900
What problem do I have?

354
00:18:10,760 --> 00:18:11,600
How are you still...

355
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:15,840
There's trouble.

356
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:17,560
Shao Nian

357
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:18,660
might have to repeat a year.

358
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:20,980
What?

359
00:18:22,560 --> 00:18:23,500
What's going on?

360
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:24,820
Where is he now?

361
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,720
He got a message from Prof. Qin.

362
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:28,300
He's probably with him now.

363
00:18:29,120 --> 00:18:29,960
I'll go find him.

364
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:31,640
Wait. You...

365
00:18:35,320 --> 00:18:36,740
Why does he have to repeat a year?

366
00:18:37,560 --> 00:18:38,760
How many classes does he attend

367
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:39,900
because of Duoduo?

368
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,280
If he has to repeat a year,

369
00:18:43,280 --> 00:18:44,620
he'll be your junior.

370
00:18:46,120 --> 00:18:47,860
I don't want a junior like him.

371
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:50,290
Hope Duoduo can talk some sense into him.

372
00:18:52,280 --> 00:18:54,340
His heart's not in his studies.

373
00:18:54,600 --> 00:18:55,860
No one can help.

374
00:18:56,760 --> 00:18:59,360
The Medical School is hard to get into.

375
00:18:59,360 --> 00:19:00,660
The tuition is expensive, too.

376
00:19:01,160 --> 00:19:02,380
He doesn't appreciate it.

377
00:19:05,520 --> 00:19:06,540
What a rich boy.

378
00:19:10,520 --> 00:19:12,000
Fifteen classes a week,

379
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,360
and you only attended five.

380
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:14,200
Tell me.

381
00:19:14,360 --> 00:19:15,460
What are you thinking?

382
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:17,700
Think before you speak.

383
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:19,620
And don't say you're doing well.

384
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:22,140
You have to meet the basic attendance.

385
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:24,760
Fine, I'll repeat then.

386
00:19:24,760 --> 00:19:26,400
That way, I can spend another year

387
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:27,560
with you.

388
00:19:27,560 --> 00:19:29,540
No, please don't.

389
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:32,820
I have nothing to teach you.

390
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:34,700
You should move on

391
00:19:35,320 --> 00:19:38,080
and annoy some other teacher.

392
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:39,900
Don't say that, Prof. Qin.

393
00:19:40,120 --> 00:19:41,700
No other teacher compares to you.

394
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,160
And besides,

395
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:45,140
in the third year, we'll start pharmacology.

396
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:46,580
I'm not ready for that.

397
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:48,980
Always have a way with words.

398
00:19:50,360 --> 00:19:51,200
Alright, alright.

399
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:53,860
Come back to class tomorrow,

400
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:56,260
and don't miss any more classes.

401
00:19:58,720 --> 00:19:59,560
Prof. Qin,

402
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:01,020
I have something tomorrow.

403
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,200
I might not make it.

404
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:03,100
How can you be so busy?

405
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:06,060
You're even busier than me.

406
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:07,280
I'm telling you.

407
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:09,500
If you keep this up, no one can't save you.

408
00:20:09,760 --> 00:20:10,600
Yes, yes.

409
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:11,900
No one can save me.

410
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:14,700
(Shao Nian often skips classes.)

411
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:16,340
(He lied to me, saying he had few classes.)

412
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:18,160
I promise

413
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:19,480
from now on,

414
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:20,340
you'll often see me in class.

415
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:21,440
Alright, Prof. Qin?

416
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:27,220
Alright. I've said enough.

417
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,060
You're not young anymore.

418
00:20:29,560 --> 00:20:31,420
You should know what to do.

419
00:20:33,040 --> 00:20:33,880
Alright, Prof. Qin.

420
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:35,320
I won't disturb you then.

421
00:20:35,320 --> 00:20:36,160
Bye-bye.

422
00:20:36,320 --> 00:20:37,160
Bye-bye.

423
00:20:41,760 --> 00:20:42,600
Duoduo.

424
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:45,640
Shao Nian.

425
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,200
We're friends, right?

426
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:49,250
We share a deep connection, right?

427
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:50,280
Of course.

428
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:51,940
Then listen to me.

429
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:55,020
Don't skip classes or miss attendance anymore.

430
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,300
You came just to say that?

431
00:20:58,080 --> 00:20:59,480
Isn't it serious enough?

432
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,060
You're at risk of not graduating.

433
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:03,480
Trust me. It's just a minor issue

434
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:04,500
that can be easily fixed.

435
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:06,580
But why are you talking like the others?

436
00:21:09,040 --> 00:21:09,880
Shao Nian,

437
00:21:10,360 --> 00:21:12,380
focus on your studies first.

438
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:13,920
If you miss too many classes,

439
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:16,000
you won't get your diploma. How can you

440
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,260
pursue your dreams without a diploma?

441
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:19,120
I heard everything you said

442
00:21:19,120 --> 00:21:20,040
to the professor.

443
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:21,500
I understand all your thoughts,

444
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:23,920
but now, you need to prioritize your studies.

445
00:21:23,920 --> 00:21:25,560
Without a diploma, what can you do?

446
00:21:25,560 --> 00:21:26,760
You need to graduate first.

447
00:21:26,760 --> 00:21:27,600
Graduate?

448
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:29,580
After graduation, there's work.

449
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:31,300
Without work, it's considered idle.

450
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:32,560
I can imagine

451
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:33,560
the excuses you'll use

452
00:21:33,560 --> 00:21:34,680
to stop me

453
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:36,080
from doing what I love.

454
00:21:36,080 --> 00:21:37,260
What did I do wrong?

455
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:38,800
Do you think

456
00:21:39,040 --> 00:21:40,300
not finishing your studies is right?

457
00:21:41,200 --> 00:21:43,260
I don't want to argue about this.

458
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:44,580
I'm leaving. Bye-bye.

459
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:51,720
Professor.

460
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:52,640
Professor.

461
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:56,220
Is Shao Nian really going to repeat a year?

462
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:58,280
Are you his girlfriend?

463
00:21:58,560 --> 00:22:00,080
- I'm not...
- If you are,

464
00:22:00,080 --> 00:22:01,860
please try to persuade him.

465
00:22:11,040 --> 00:22:12,280
I can provide

466
00:22:12,280 --> 00:22:13,480
a few more pieces

467
00:22:13,480 --> 00:22:14,320
for you to look at.

468
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:15,560
Right. If possible,

469
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:17,140
I'd like to study oil painting with you.

470
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,480
Right.

471
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:20,020
Sure. Thanks.

472
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:25,840
Coach Lu.

473
00:22:28,280 --> 00:22:30,540
Shao Nian, aren't you the team doctor?

474
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,600
Shouldn't you be studying medicine?

475
00:22:32,600 --> 00:22:34,180
Are you running a side business?

476
00:22:34,920 --> 00:22:36,120
Coach Lu, what are you doing here?

477
00:22:36,120 --> 00:22:36,960
Just wandering around.

478
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:40,520
Well, keep wandering.

479
00:22:40,520 --> 00:22:41,880
If you need anything, text me.

480
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:43,480
Please don't tell anyone

481
00:22:43,480 --> 00:22:44,520
about today.

482
00:22:44,520 --> 00:22:45,460
No problem.

483
00:22:45,680 --> 00:22:46,720
I'm here as a coach,

484
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:48,140
not a professor.

485
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,840
Alright, thank you.

486
00:22:49,840 --> 00:22:50,680
Bye-bye.

487
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:51,640
I'm leaving now.

488
00:22:56,120 --> 00:22:57,300
So secretive.

489
00:23:13,280 --> 00:23:14,120
Shao Nian.

490
00:23:15,530 --> 00:23:16,740
Open the door, Shao Nian.

491
00:23:17,130 --> 00:23:18,020
Shao Nian.

492
00:23:18,840 --> 00:23:19,680
The door's unlocked.

493
00:23:36,200 --> 00:23:37,820
You really don't want to go to class, huh?

494
00:23:39,320 --> 00:23:40,760
Did you see my face

495
00:23:40,760 --> 00:23:41,780
when you mentioned class?

496
00:23:42,800 --> 00:23:44,620
Alright. I won't mention class anymore.

497
00:23:45,280 --> 00:23:47,300
I'm not angry about you mentioning class.

498
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:49,080
Forget it.

499
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:52,020
I know why you're upset.

500
00:23:53,280 --> 00:23:54,900
It's because I didn't support you,

501
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:56,080
right?

502
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,580
You figured that out, huh?

503
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:02,940
I've deeply reflected on my actions.

504
00:24:03,240 --> 00:24:04,120
As your good friend

505
00:24:04,120 --> 00:24:05,420
and mentor,

506
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:06,840
I feel it's my duty

507
00:24:06,840 --> 00:24:08,020
to help and support your dreams.

508
00:24:11,800 --> 00:24:12,640
How will you do that?

509
00:24:18,900 --> 00:24:21,580
(Dafu BBQ)

510
00:24:32,040 --> 00:24:32,880
Does this work?

511
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:34,440
Yes.

512
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:38,860
I'm a bit nervous. No one's painted me before.

513
00:24:40,460 --> 00:24:42,760
♪Who's laughing around♪

514
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,660
Should I be

515
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:46,780
holding something while you paint?

516
00:24:47,040 --> 00:24:47,880
My hands feel empty.

517
00:24:47,890 --> 00:24:49,360
Should I hold something?

518
00:24:49,360 --> 00:24:50,820
No need. It's fine as is.

519
00:24:54,720 --> 00:24:55,560
A vase.

520
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:57,240
This looks good.

521
00:24:57,760 --> 00:24:58,600
Like this.

522
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:01,100
Very elegant.

523
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:03,420
A dignified feeling.

524
00:25:04,610 --> 00:25:07,080
♪You run bravely♪

525
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:09,060
No, not good.

526
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:10,760
Let me get something else.

527
00:25:10,760 --> 00:25:11,660
Wait a moment.

528
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:16,300
This, this.

529
00:25:16,300 --> 00:25:18,440
♪Look at you messing around♪

530
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:19,280
An orange.

531
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:20,560
This is good.

532
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:22,540
- Is this okay?
- Yes.

533
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:24,540
Like this?

534
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:26,360
Yes.

535
00:25:27,430 --> 00:25:29,690
♪See tomorrow's tide♪

536
00:25:30,040 --> 00:25:32,100
Will this orange make my face look too yellow?

537
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:33,760
No. The orange is yellow.

538
00:25:33,760 --> 00:25:34,640
So it would make me

539
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,860
look even more yellow.

540
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:40,240
I'll switch it. Just one last time.

541
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:41,780
Wait, wait.

542
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:45,480
Duoduo, if you keep running around,

543
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:46,500
I won't paint you anymore.

544
00:25:50,080 --> 00:25:51,280
Are you here to be painted

545
00:25:51,280 --> 00:25:52,200
or to eat?

546
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:54,320
This is good. This is the real me.

547
00:25:54,320 --> 00:25:56,360
Alright, hold still. Don't move.

548
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:57,200
Okay.

549
00:25:59,500 --> 00:26:03,070
♪The dream is amazing like the stars♪

550
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:05,780
It smells so good.

551
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:11,300
Are you eating now?

552
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:13,680
It smells so good. Right in front of me.

553
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:14,600
Tempting me.

554
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:15,480
Who can resist?

555
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,600
You try it. You can't resist.

556
00:26:16,600 --> 00:26:17,480
- Try one.
- No, no.

557
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:18,700
You've been working so hard. Try one.

558
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:20,920
Let me see.

559
00:26:22,680 --> 00:26:23,760
What are you painting?

560
00:26:23,760 --> 00:26:24,960
Is my face that big?

561
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:26,160
It looks nice.

562
00:26:26,160 --> 00:26:27,680
My arms aren't that thick either.

563
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:28,920
They're not thick at all.

564
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:30,160
Keep painting.

565
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:31,340
Can you stay still for a bit?

566
00:26:31,430 --> 00:26:33,770
♪See tomorrow's tide♪

567
00:26:33,770 --> 00:26:36,240
♪I like every second of you♪

568
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:37,080
So delicious.

569
00:26:39,360 --> 00:26:40,880
Hold still. Don't move.

570
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:42,160
You can paint even if I move.

571
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:43,000
I trust your skills.

572
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:43,940
You can do it.

573
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:47,670
♪You let me know♪

574
00:26:50,120 --> 00:26:51,120
How much longer?

575
00:26:51,120 --> 00:26:52,120
Almost done.

576
00:26:55,260 --> 00:26:56,240
It's so good.

577
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,260
Do you want the last one?

578
00:26:58,120 --> 00:26:59,000
You eat it.

579
00:26:59,000 --> 00:26:59,840
Try one. Try one.

580
00:26:59,850 --> 00:27:01,100
Eat it, and stop moving. Please.

581
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:03,300
- Hurry.
- Missing an eye.

582
00:27:08,280 --> 00:27:10,060
You've packed your bags.

583
00:27:10,280 --> 00:27:11,600
Are you planning to leave?

584
00:27:11,600 --> 00:27:12,460
Come on.

