875
00:38:41,200 --> 00:38:42,380
No more explanations.

876
00:38:43,080 --> 00:38:45,420
Pack your things and leave.

877
00:38:46,160 --> 00:38:47,240
I can't let you stay with our team.

878
00:38:47,240 --> 00:38:48,640
Shao Nian, hold on.

879
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:50,120
Let's talk this over. Have a seat.

880
00:38:50,120 --> 00:38:51,320
There's nothing to discuss between us.

881
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,940
- There is.
- We don't need a liar.

882
00:38:53,310 --> 00:38:54,160
Wait.

883
00:38:54,160 --> 00:38:55,460
There really is.

884
00:38:56,560 --> 00:38:57,460
Listen to me.

885
00:38:58,600 --> 00:38:59,620
One minute.

886
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:01,600
Think about it.

887
00:39:02,520 --> 00:39:03,360
You were the one

888
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:04,660
who brought me here.

889
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:08,740
You told everyone I was Coach Lu Daxing

890
00:39:09,520 --> 00:39:11,220
from the National Youth Team,

891
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:13,080
especially in front of Li Guoduo.

892
00:39:13,080 --> 00:39:14,140
You made a big deal out of it.

893
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:17,860
If you expose me

894
00:39:18,680 --> 00:39:19,540
and kick me out now,

895
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:21,160
what will you do?

896
00:39:23,120 --> 00:39:24,260
Besides,

897
00:39:25,040 --> 00:39:26,560
sports

898
00:39:26,560 --> 00:39:27,900
are interconnected.

899
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:29,860
I'm into windsurfing,

900
00:39:31,520 --> 00:39:33,180
but it's still relevant.

901
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:35,800
And

902
00:39:37,680 --> 00:39:38,520
Lu Daxing

903
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:41,020
really is my cousin.

904
00:39:42,720 --> 00:39:44,460
I can help you with him.

905
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:50,580
Let's help each other out.

906
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:01,800
What?

907
00:40:02,120 --> 00:40:03,460
Coach Lu is an impostor?

908
00:40:05,040 --> 00:40:05,880
I knew it.

909
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:07,620
The National Youth Team is better than this.

910
00:40:08,200 --> 00:40:10,500
I knew it. Lu Xiaole wasn't reliable.

911
00:40:11,160 --> 00:40:12,620
It's delayed your training.

912
00:40:13,200 --> 00:40:15,580
I'll tell everyone tomorrow.

913
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:18,320
Bro, you've put yourself

914
00:40:18,320 --> 00:40:19,660
in a tough spot.

915
00:40:20,600 --> 00:40:22,140
What if word gets out

916
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:23,720
that you couldn't get a coach

917
00:40:23,720 --> 00:40:25,280
from the National Youth Team

918
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,980
and brought in a fake on purpose?

919
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:28,040
That would be disastrous.

920
00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:30,580
But we can't keep it a secret.

921
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:32,860
Don't worry, bro.

922
00:40:33,120 --> 00:40:34,160
I think

923
