929
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:47,580
but we can't control

930
00:40:47,780 --> 00:40:48,790
how the other team members feel.

931
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:50,440
And think about it.

932
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:51,660
If the school finds out,

933
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:53,980
our team might get disbanded.

934
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:56,360
He's supposed to be the coach,

935
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:58,220
but if he's only focusing

936
00:40:58,600 --> 00:40:59,640
on physical training,

937
00:40:59,640 --> 00:41:01,100
it's wasting our time.

938
00:41:02,200 --> 00:41:03,130
You can't think of it like that.

939
00:41:03,720 --> 00:41:05,100
You had good intentions.

940
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:07,460
Things just didn't go as planned.

941
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:10,060
Actually,

942
00:41:10,560 --> 00:41:12,020
as long as the result is good,

943
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:14,080
no one will care about the process.

944
00:41:14,080 --> 00:41:16,380
Right, the result is what matters.

945
00:41:28,680 --> 00:41:29,620
What do you mean?

946
00:41:30,240 --> 00:41:31,080
Lu Xiaole,

947
00:41:31,200 --> 00:41:32,420
I borrowed all the books

948
00:41:32,680 --> 00:41:34,080
about beach volleyball

949
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:35,300
