950
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:36,640
And here's

951
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:38,580
some material I copied from Gao.

952
00:41:39,040 --> 00:41:40,300
You have a week

953
00:41:40,560 --> 00:41:41,780
