958
00:41:49,960 --> 00:41:50,940
- You...
- I don't want to hear it.

959
00:41:51,560 --> 00:41:52,400
Memorize it all

960
00:41:52,760 --> 00:41:53,740
and come up with a strategy.

961
00:41:54,240 --> 00:41:55,080
Otherwise...

962
