969
00:42:17,840 --> 00:42:18,680
Hey.

970
00:42:18,880 --> 00:42:20,340
Why are you laughing by yourself?

971
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:23,700
That's not laughing.

972
00:42:27,240 --> 00:42:28,820
It seems like you changed

973
00:42:29,520 --> 00:42:31,400
after finding out

974
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:32,700
that Coach Lu is fake.

975
00:42:35,480 --> 00:42:36,840
How did it go

976
00:42:36,840 --> 00:42:37,680
