977
00:42:38,120 --> 00:42:39,180
It's done.

978
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:41,640
Shao Nian and I put those books

979
00:42:41,640 --> 00:42:43,100
outside Coach Lu's door.

980
00:42:44,360 --> 00:42:45,560
Well.

981
00:42:45,560 --> 00:42:47,520
The fake coach.

982
00:42:47,520 --> 00:42:48,660
I was exhausted.

983
00:42:49,200 --> 00:42:50,040
Alright.

984
00:42:50,440 --> 00:42:52,960
Shao Nian must treat us someday

985
00:42:52,960 --> 00:42:54,720
for the trouble we went through

986
00:42:54,720 --> 00:42:55,940
helping him appease Li Guoduo.

987
00:42:57,800 --> 00:42:58,940
I'd really appreciate it.

